{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Okay, I have no idea what we're going to play."},{"time":3000,"text":"I won't be able to tell you what it is until it happens."},{"time":6000,"text":"I didn't realize there was going to be a little music before."},{"time":9000,"text":"So I think I'm going to start with what I just heard."}]},{"cues":[{"time":11000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":346000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":355000,"text":"Okay, so first of all,"},{"time":357000,"text":"let's welcome Mr. Jamire Williams on the drums,"},{"time":360000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":363000,"text":"Burniss Travis on the bass,"},{"time":365000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":367000,"text":"and Mr. Christian Sands on the piano."}]},{"cues":[{"time":370000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":373000,"text":"So the bandstand, as we call it,"},{"time":375000,"text":"this is an incredible space."},{"time":377000,"text":"It is really a sacred space."},{"time":379000,"text":"And one of the things that is really sacred about it"},{"time":381000,"text":"is that you have no opportunity to think about the future,"},{"time":384000,"text":"or the past."},{"time":386000,"text":"You really are alive right here in this moment."},{"time":388000,"text":"There are so many decisions being made"},{"time":390000,"text":"when you walk on the bandstand."},{"time":392000,"text":"We had no idea what key we were going to play in."},{"time":395000,"text":"In the middle, we sort of made our way"},{"time":397000,"text":"into a song called \"Titi Boom.\""},{"time":399000,"text":"But that could have happened -- maybe, maybe not."},{"time":402000,"text":"Everyone's listening. We're responding."},{"time":404000,"text":"You have no time for projected ideas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":406000,"text":"So the idea of a mistake:"},{"time":409000,"text":"From the perspective of a jazz musician,"},{"time":411000,"text":"it's easier to talk about someone else's mistake."},{"time":416000,"text":"So the way I perceive a mistake when I'm on the bandstand --"},{"time":419000,"text":"first of all, we don't really see it as a mistake."},{"time":421000,"text":"The only mistake lies"},{"time":423000,"text":"in that I'm not able to perceive"},{"time":425000,"text":"what it is that someone else did."},{"time":427000,"text":"Every \"mistake\" is an opportunity in jazz."},{"time":430000,"text":"So it's hard to even describe"},{"time":432000,"text":"what a funny note would be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":434000,"text":"So for example, if I played a color, like we were playing on a palette,"},{"time":437000,"text":"that sounded like this ..."},{"time":439000,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":441000,"text":"So if Christian played a note -- like play an F."},{"time":444000,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":446000,"text":"See, these are all right inside of the color palette."},{"time":449000,"text":"If you played an E."},{"time":452000,"text":"See, these all lie right inside"},{"time":454000,"text":"of this general emotional palette that we were painting."},{"time":456000,"text":"If you played an F# though,"},{"time":458000,"text":"(Dissonance)"},{"time":462000,"text":"to most people's ears, they would perceive that as a mistake."}]},{"cues":[{"time":465000,"text":"So I'm going to show you, we're going to play just for a second."},{"time":467000,"text":"And we're going to play on this palette."},{"time":469000,"text":"And at some point, Christian will introduce this note."},{"time":471000,"text":"And we won't react to it."},{"time":473000,"text":"He'll introduce it for a second"},{"time":475000,"text":"and then I'll stop, I'll talk for a second."},{"time":477000,"text":"We'll see what happens when we play with this palette."}]},{"cues":[{"time":479000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":504000,"text":"So someone could conceptually perceive that as a mistake."},{"time":508000,"text":"The only way that I would say it was a mistake"},{"time":510000,"text":"is in that we didn't react to it."},{"time":512000,"text":"It was an opportunity that was missed."},{"time":514000,"text":"So it's unpredictable. We'll paint this palette again."},{"time":517000,"text":"He'll play it. I don't know how we'll react to it, but something will change."},{"time":520000,"text":"We'll all accept his ideas,"},{"time":522000,"text":"or not."}]},{"cues":[{"time":524000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":593000,"text":"So you see, he played this note."},{"time":595000,"text":"I ended up creating a melody out of it."},{"time":597000,"text":"The texture changed in the drums this time."},{"time":599000,"text":"It got a little bit more rhythmic, a little bit more intense"},{"time":602000,"text":"in response to how I responded to it."},{"time":604000,"text":"So there is no mistake."},{"time":606000,"text":"The only mistake is if I'm not aware,"},{"time":608000,"text":"if each individual musician is not aware"},{"time":610000,"text":"and accepting enough of his fellow band member"},{"time":614000,"text":"to incorporate the idea and we don't allow for creativity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":617000,"text":"So jazz, this bandstand is absolutely amazing."},{"time":621000,"text":"It's a very purifying experience."},{"time":623000,"text":"And I know that I speak for all of us when I tell you that we don't take it for granted."},{"time":626000,"text":"We know that to be able to come on the bandstand and play music is a blessing."},{"time":630000,"text":"So how does this all relate to behavioral finance?"},{"time":633000,"text":"Well we're jazz musicians,"},{"time":635000,"text":"so stereotypically we don't have a great relationship to finance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":637000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":640000,"text":"Anyway, I just wanted to sort of point out the way that we handle it."},{"time":643000,"text":"And the other dynamic of it"},{"time":645000,"text":"is that we don't micromanage in jazz."},{"time":648000,"text":"You have some people who do."},{"time":650000,"text":"But what that does"},{"time":652000,"text":"is it actually limits the artistic possibilities."},{"time":654000,"text":"If I come up and I dictate to the band"},{"time":657000,"text":"that I want to play like this and I want the music to go this way,"},{"time":659000,"text":"and I just jump right in ..."},{"time":661000,"text":"ready, just play some time."},{"time":663000,"text":"One, two, one, two, three, four."},{"time":665000,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":677000,"text":"It's kind of chaotic because I'm bullying my ideas."},{"time":679000,"text":"I'm telling them, \"You come with me over this way.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":681000,"text":"If I really want the music to go there,"},{"time":683000,"text":"the best way for me to do it is to listen."},{"time":685000,"text":"This is a science of listening."},{"time":687000,"text":"It has far more to do with what I can perceive"},{"time":689000,"text":"than what it is that I can do."},{"time":691000,"text":"So if I want the music to get to a certain level of intensity,"},{"time":694000,"text":"the first step for me is"},{"time":696000,"text":"to be patient, to listen to what's going on"},{"time":698000,"text":"and pull from something that's going on around me."},{"time":701000,"text":"When you do that, you engage and inspire the other musicians"},{"time":704000,"text":"and they give you more, and gradually it builds."},{"time":706000,"text":"Watch. One, two, a one, two, three, four."}]},{"cues":[{"time":709000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":749000,"text":"Totally different experience when I'm pulling ideas."},{"time":752000,"text":"It's much more organic. It's much more nuanced."},{"time":754000,"text":"It's not about bullying my vision or anything like that."},{"time":756000,"text":"It's about being here in the moment,"},{"time":758000,"text":"accepting one another"},{"time":760000,"text":"and allowing creativity to flow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":762000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":764000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}